This directory contains Xlib examples using the XDraw command.

bounce			Open Look only, a colorful demo of line 
			drawing and scaling.

explode			An Open Look demo program, moving text and
			gravity on small dots.

graph.sh		A library of functions that can be attached to
			either an OPEN LOOK stub or Motif DrawingArea
			widget as the expose event handler.  These
			functions draw simple pie or bar charts or
			legends.

olpietst, xmpietst	OPEN LOOK and Motif examples of how to use
			the pie chart function from graph.sh.

olbartst, xmbartst	OPEN LOOK and Motif examples of how to use
			the bar chart function from graph.sh.
